---
title: Scenario 2 — Normal Order Change / FLIP (Happy Path)
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Service as Backend Service
    participant Cache as SourceCache
    participant Sub as Throttled Subscription\n(150ms)
    participant Box as OrderedAnimatedListBox
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline
    participant FLIP as FLIP Engine

    Service->>Cache: Update item.Order

    Note over Sub: Throttle window starts\nMore order changes may arrive\nand be collapsed here

    Sub-->>Box: CollectionChanged (Move) after 150ms

    Box->>Box: ClassifyChange\nHasAnyPendingReason() = false\ne.Action = Move\n→ ChangeType.OrderChange

    alt Queue is empty and pipeline idle
        Box->>Pipeline: Enqueue OrderChange snapshot
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: TryProcessNext\n_pipelineBusy = true
    else Previous OrderChange already queued
        Box->>Pipeline: Replace last OrderChange\n(collapse to latest state)
        Note over Pipeline: Only final order state matters\nIntermediate states discarded
    end

    Pipeline->>Box: ProcessSnapshot(OrderChange)
    Box->>FLIP: OnBeforeAnimatedDiff()\nCapturePreLayoutBounds()
    Note over FLIP: Snapshot: {A→(0,0), B→(0,40), C→(0,80), D→(0,120)}
    Note over FLIP: capturedGeneration = ++_flipGeneration

    Box->>Box: DiffVisible(newOrder)\nVisibleItems.Move(2→0)\nObservableCollection raises Move event\nListBox re-layouts

    Note over Box: Layout now reflects new order\nContainers at new physical positions

    FLIP->>FLIP: Post ApplyFlip at DispatcherPriority.Render

    Note over FLIP: Render pass completes\nApplyFlip fires

    FLIP->>FLIP: Check capturedGeneration == _flipGeneration\n(no newer refresh arrived — proceed)

    loop For each item that moved
        FLIP->>FLIP: Read new position from layout
        Note over FLIP: B is now at (0,0) but was at (0,40)\ndx=0, dy=40
        FLIP->>FLIP: container.Translate.Y = +40  [snap to old pos]
        FLIP->>FLIP: RunAnimation: Translate.Y 40 → 0
        Note over FLIP: Item appears to animate\nfrom its old position to its new one
    end

    FLIP->>FLIP: _inflightCount reaches 0
    Box->>Pipeline: OnAllAnimationsComplete\n_pipelineBusy = false
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: TryProcessNext (queue empty — done)
